---
title: Roast Beef Eye Fillet & Mustard Gravy with Garlic Mash & Bacon Greens
description: Tender perfection, that’s how people will describe this dinner once they’re done licking their plates! This premium cut of beef is roasted until juicy and flavourful, and is paired with a fragrant garlic mash, bacon-speckled greens and a punchy Dijon gravy. Tonight’s dinner will have the aftertaste of satisfaction.
